text: Used to love this Papa Murphy's for last-minute teen-feeding needs. Now it's an empty storefront with a For Lease sign. Next nearest Papa Murphy's is > 2 miles away.

text: Loves me some Papa Murphy's.  Clean store nice and polite staff

name: Goggle User
text: I noticed that the other Goggle reviews are a couple of years old and since employees and food quality often changes over time here is a current review. The pizza tastes pretty good and it is made fresh within minutes of when I pick it up. ‚Ä¶More

name: Raeben Nolan
text: Rude high-school-aged employees. I get a ton of coupons for this location but still feeling like I'd rather just pay more money for real pizza (also, SE Portland is the epicenter of excellent pizza so why do I even come here?). Coupons don't cancel out rudeness.
